*Glup* je rekao da nema nikog drugog. (He said something stupid that there was nobody else.)

*Glupo* je da me ljudi tako gledaju. (It's stupid that people look at me like that.)

*Glupom* se smeju svi. (Everybody laughs at the fool.)

*Gluposti* su sve što je izgovorio. (Everything he said were foolishness.)

*Glupača* je postala pred svima. (She became a fool in front of everybody.)

*Glupošću* je zasenio sve. (He overshadowed everyone with his foolishness.)